# warehouse_map.pcd
#
# PCD (Point Cloud Data) placeholder — 3-D map of the warehouse environment
# produced by the SLAM front-end node during a manual survey run.
#
# Format:    PCD v0.7
# Fields:    x y z intensity
# Size:      4 4 4 4
# Type:      F F F F
# Count:     1 1 1 1
# Width:     125000      (number of points)
# Height:    1           (unorganised cloud)
# Viewpoint: 0 0 0 1 0 0 0
# Points:    125000
# Data:      binary_compressed
#
# This file would be produced by:
#   ros2 run pcl_ros pointcloud_to_pcd  (with cloud topic /map/pointcloud)
# or by the slam_frontend_node save_map service call.
#
# Approximate real-world extents:
#   X: -15 m to +15 m (30 m wide)
#   Y: -12 m to +12 m (24 m deep)
#   Z:  0 m  to  6 m  (ceiling height)
